		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">放置「风息花」后，大林猪红温，自身<span color="#ffbfbf">攻击力提升30%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">大林猪在场地中央连续大跳5次，每次造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
